       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CTRLDEC01.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-BASE-SALARY      PIC S9(5)V99 VALUE 125.75.
       01 WS-EMPLOYEE-COUNT    PIC 9(3) VALUE 8.
       01 WS-TAX-RATE          PIC S9V9(4) VALUE +0.1887.
       01 WS-GROSS-SALARY      PIC S9(7)V99.
       01 WS-TAX-AMOUNT        PIC S9(7)V99.
       01 WS-NET-SALARY        PIC S9(7)V99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           COMPUTE WS-GROSS-SALARY = WS-BASE-SALARY * WS-EMPLOYEE-COUNT
           COMPUTE WS-TAX-AMOUNT = WS-GROSS-SALARY * WS-TAX-RATE

           IF WS-TAX-AMOUNT > 100.00
               DISPLAY "TAX FLAGGED"
           ELSE
               DISPLAY "TAX NORMAL"
           END-IF

           COMPUTE WS-NET-SALARY = WS-GROSS-SALARY - WS-TAX-AMOUNT
           DISPLAY "GROSS=" WS-GROSS-SALARY
           DISPLAY "TAX=" WS-TAX-AMOUNT
           DISPLAY "NET=" WS-NET-SALARY
           STOP RUN.
